
PRODUCTION
++++++++++

SUMMARY
-------
Controls the production mode option.

SYNTAX
------

  ``PRODUCTION ON|OFF``

INPUT
-----
   :ON:  Turn production mode option on.
    
   :OFF:  Turn production mode option off.
    
DEFAULT VALUES
--------------

  ``PROD OFF``

DESCRIPTION
-----------
   When this option is on, fatal errors terminate SAC immediately.  When this
   option if off, control is returned to the terminal after fatal errors.

LATEST REVISION
---------------
   January 8, 1983 (Version 8.0)

